data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in East Edmond's Fox Lake Addition. Neighborhood Pond, Pool, and Playground. This stunning property is perfectly situated just minutes away from I-35 for easy commuting. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious formal dining and living area. To your right, you'll find a large study with built-in bookcases. The owner's suite boasts a huge walk-in closet with built-ins, double sink vanity, jetted tub, and a large shower.  There are two more bedrooms and a bathroom located on the north side of the house. The south side features forth bedroom and bathroom, as well as an extra living space that could be used as a mother-in-law suite.  The home features beautiful tile and wood throughout. A chef's kitchen is a dream come true with its double oven air fryer, gas stove, microwave oven, trash compactor, granite countertops and breakfast bar. There's also a large pantry and plenty of counter for meal prep. The kitchen opens up to the family room, which overlooks the backyard. An additional full bathroom and bedroom upstairs provide even more space for guests not included in the 3032 SQFT. The home has a great floor plan with lots of space both inside and out, including a pergola covered patio that's perfect for family gatherings.
